73
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:39,960
I will save my investigating what you are going around doing for later.

74
00:08:41,290 --> 00:08:43,710
Where's Ji Oh right now?

75
00:08:53,110 --> 00:08:55,530
Shall we start with you in handcuffs?

76
00:09:00,490 --> 00:09:02,200
You're treating me like a criminal.

77
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,700
Are you afraid?

78
00:09:03,700 --> 00:09:06,260
Shall I start in handcuffs?

79
00:09:15,300 --> 00:09:17,300
Let's start.

80
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:57,780
Ji Oh, it's me.

81
00:09:57,780 --> 00:09:59,980
Do you remember?

82
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:03,450
Don't you remember me?

83
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:18,250
It's alright, Ji Oh.

84
00:10:19,770 --> 00:10:21,890
You're back home.

85
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:26,110
This is our home.

86
00:10:26,110 --> 00:10:28,460
Don't talk nonsense.

87
00:10:33,610 --> 00:10:35,650
Ji Oh.

88
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:39,640
I'm sorry I left you alone for so long.

89
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:41,220
You must have been very lonely.

90
00:10:41,220 --> 00:10:43,520
Who are you?

91
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:47,130
I thought I lost you forever.

92
00:10:47,130 --> 00:10:49,370
Just who are you?

93
00:10:58,370 --> 00:11:00,410
I am,

94
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:05,090
your father.

95
00:11:15,990 --> 00:11:18,270
And you're my son.

96
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:28,520
Don't we need to tie him up?

97
00:11:28,520 --> 00:11:31,000
- He already is. 
- Where?

98
00:11:33,310 --> 00:11:38,010
You don't think we can physically tie him up and drag him to the lab by force, do you?

99
00:11:38,010 --> 00:11:42,250
