100
00:11:42,250 --> 00:11:46,380
By sweet talking to him saying that he's the father, he's simply disarming him.

101
00:11:46,380 --> 00:11:49,640
I must say Dr. Ryu is truly  the epitome of evil.

102
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:54,100
Would you like a glass of water?

103
00:11:54,100 --> 00:11:55,730
You little-

104
