I do.

145
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:19,750
Can I meet him? I want to.

146
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:22,170
He's the only one I can trust.

147
00:14:22,170 --> 00:14:25,190
Before I meet him and hear from him, I'm not going to trust anyone.

148
00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:29,440
You're seeing him right now.

149
00:14:33,410 --> 00:14:35,740
I'm Ryu Jung Kwon.

150
00:14:37,930 --> 00:14:40,690
You even forgot your father's name.

151
00:14:46,810 --> 00:14:49,030
I'm sure you have many questions for me.

152
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:51,430
Why was I abandoned?

153
00:14:51,430 --> 00:14:53,180
Why didn't you come and look for me sooner?

154
00:14:53,180 --> 00:14:56,270
Why did you hunt me down as if you were going to kill me?

155
00:14:56,270 --> 00:14:58,290
Why am I different from others?

156
00:14:58,290 --> 00:15:01,600
Am I, perhaps, a monster?

157
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:05,860
None of that is important.

158
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:09,380
Am I capable of loving someone?

159
00:15:10,560 --> 00:15:14,630
Apart from that question, all others are mere gabarge.

160
00:15:14,630 --> 00:15:17,490
I risked my whole life

161
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:21,730
on loving you.

162
00:15:21,730 --> 00:15:25,020
You're the only one I love.

163
00:15:27,720 --> 00:15:30,850
Hence, I'm not asking any questions.

164
00:15:32,550 --> 00:15:35,150
Why did you leave me?

165
00:15:36,460 --> 00:15:39,440
