167
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,600
Do you think he's here?

168
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:09,460
I doubt it.

169
00:16:09,460 --> 00:16:11,050
But why are we here?

170
00:16:11,050 --> 00:16:13,160
I thought maybe.

171
00:16:33,740 --> 00:16:35,580
He isn't here.

172
00:16:35,580 --> 00:16:38,990
