209
00:19:27,180 --> 00:19:31,050
-Ha Yeong Jae. 
 -Ha Yeong Jae.

210
00:19:31,050 --> 00:19:34,160
Was it Haneul Ae Gu Reum?

211
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:37,790
He liked to show me the pictures of his daughter and bragged.

212
00:19:46,220 --> 00:19:48,700
What happened to him?

213
00:19:48,700 --> 00:19:52,480
He set the lab on fire. Then he took you and ran away.

214
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:55,410
You didn't resist and followed him obediently.

215
00:19:55,410 --> 00:19:57,220
 Catch them! 

216
00:20:08,420 --> 00:20:10,410
He tried to sell you off.

217
00:20:10,410 --> 00:20:12,580
Why would he want to sell me off?

218
00:20:13,650 --> 00:20:15,800
Because you're special.

219
00:20:15,800 --> 00:20:18,780
You were much coveted as a living and breathing object to be experimented on.

220
00:20:18,780 --> 00:20:22,480
-Then what? 
 -You know the rest.

221
00:20:22,480 --> 00:20:25,600
I'm aware that you met with the daughter of Ha Yeong Jae.

222
00:20:27,940 --> 00:20:30,950
Did I- did I kill him?

223
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:38,410
You have the power to kill anyone.

224
00:20:38,410 --> 00:20:41,800
