229
00:20:52,540 --> 00:20:54,470
Not to mention, the rainbows.

230
00:20:54,470 --> 00:20:57,450
He moved you with the sweet words of his.

231
00:20:58,600 --> 00:21:01,840
You aren't anyone who can kill those you're fond of.

232
00:21:01,840 --> 00:21:04,270
Then, who killed him?

233
00:21:06,140 --> 00:21:08,710
It's time.

234
00:21:08,710 --> 00:21:11,680
- How is he?
-  His recovery rate and ability to regenerate

235
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:14,660
is ten times as much as that of a normal human being.

236
00:21:16,080 --> 00:21:18,040
Great.

237
00:21:33,210 --> 00:21:34,880
I'll tell you everything later.

238
00:21:34,880 --> 00:21:36,180
