241
00:21:42,770 --> 00:21:45,540
Remember what I, your father, tell you.

242
00:21:45,540 --> 00:21:47,010
You have to find the answer.

243
00:21:47,010 --> 00:21:48,610
What answer?

244
00:21:48,610 --> 00:21:51,630
Is the existence of the human race justified?

245
00:21:53,180 --> 00:21:56,660
Are we going to be  the last generation of the human race?

246
00:21:57,800 --> 00:22:01,580
Two questions, but one answer.

247
00:22:01,580 --> 00:22:04,150
Before you find the answer,

248
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:08,780
you must withstand all that comes your way no matter how hard.

249
00:22:24,070 --> 00:22:25,610
What is it?

250
00:22:30,450 --> 00:22:32,350
Who are you?

251
00:22:42,730 --> 00:22:44,620
You—

252
00:22:44,620 --> 00:22:46,750
What are you?

253
00:22:47,950 --> 00:22:51,410
I'll kill you. I'll kill you!

254
00:23:05,650 --> 00:23:07,460
No!

255
00:23:12,170 --> 00:23:14,870
Ah, F-Father!

256
00:23:29,490 --> 00:23:32,150
Wow, he's incredible!

257
00:23:32,150 --> 00:23:35,210
That's enough to take down an elephant.

